Vegan Ranch Dressing
  --America's Test Kitchen

1/2 c vegan mayonnaise
2 tbsp unsweetened plain coconut milk yogurt
1 tsp white wine vinegar
1 1/2 tsp minced fresh chives
1 1/2 tsp fresh dill
1/4 tsp garlic powder
1/8 tsp salt
1/8 tsp pepper

Whisk all ingredients in bowl until smooth. Can be refrigerated for up to 4 days.
